{"tid":2159140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"篩選傳媒採訪 警死撐溝通延誤","createTime":"2020-08-16T06:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T06:48:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6f3a9a7aeea575b1ccff57ec995969fa1bd6a54d","tid":2159140,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:48:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/3XOPNFHQRZFUBD43KM53E7PFOA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2F3XOPNFHQRZFUBD43KM53E7PFOA%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJDyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=1610dccb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2F3XOPNFHQRZFUBD43KM53E7PFOA%2F&h=2dac8dc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/3XOPNFHQRZFUBD43KM53E7PFOA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n篩選傳媒採訪 警死撐溝通延誤<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZLfToNCPiSAYJlpp45L2DD64A8E=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XQ2LTCT3Q5EBHJWBK4F5ZY2Y6I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZLfToNCPiSAYJlpp45L2DD64A8E%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXQ2LTCT3Q5EBHJWBK4F5ZY2Y6I.jpg&h=b4ff0236&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警方周一搜查《蘋果日報》，多間傳媒被拒進入封鎖區採訪。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】周一警方大舉闖入《蘋果日報》大樓，曾篩選傳媒採訪，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記協斥轉移視線<br />\n<br />\n記協主席楊健興指斥警方轉移視線，「完全錯晒方向」，批評警方未有認清問題關鍵，並非某間媒體無法採訪，而是警方不應出現以媒體規模大小、報道是否持平、過往是否合作等主觀判斷，篩選某些「可信傳媒」採訪，「我哋理解，政府公開講對傳媒、媒體採訪都係講公平公正，基本上如果有佢認可證件嘅，包括傳媒機構、記協、攝協，有啲場合係嗰啲先入到去嘅，再冇區分合唔合作，或者持唔持平，如果再咁落去，係無咗個制度，唔係講法治」。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。；楊健興指業界已幾乎一面倒反對，要求停止篩選。"}]}